CombsBot - bot for #catacombs.
Features:
  o Will query wicker's database for the following requested info:
    - IP to hostname / hostname to IP
    - hostname / IP -> Purpose
    - hostname / IP -> Hardware
    - hostname / IP -> OS
  o Commands
    - CombsBot:
        o host $hostname / $IP
        o purpose $hostname / $IP
        o hardware $hostname / $IP
        o os $hostname / $IP
